ed by Jack, specially adapted for our Wounded Warriors. By doing this, the Governor is attacking the United States Air Force, and our Military, not a smart thing to do. These Courses exist, they are terrible, Jack Nicklaus will make them GREAT. Why should the Air Force and other Military personnel be forced to wait through a long Legal Review process and, perhaps, even more so, why should Wounded Warriors be forced to travel long distances to play Golf somewhere else or, worse yet, not play Golf at all. Our Soldiers and Veterans deserve THE BEST \u2014 NO WAITING, NO GAMES! Thank you for your attention to this matter. President DONALD J. TRUMP", "large_image": "jlEvdn0qfyInnyTh.png", "title": "Donald J. Trump (@realDonaldTrump)"}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsnDJDtJ", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 28, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8663471, "raw_content": "", "author": "MEME-SUPREME", "created": 1780757295488, "profile_picture": "in2RwAS4UU0c", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.patriots.win", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsnDJDtJ.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.patriots.win/post/xckdPmceFS4E.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/SPQLGfjKfYQkiWWx.jpeg", "width": 768, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 768}], "blurhash": "UADm:%ofE,WB04kBT1jF}MWCNes,KAaybIoe", "full_resolution": [1280, 1280]}, "title": "This is my pride flag.", "last_comment_created": 1780757295485, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 0, "score_up": 28, "is_edited": false, "is_modera